<h1>Weighted Down</h1>

<p>A really simple way to track what you're eating, and how much you weigh.</p>
<p>It's free to use - so don't worry if you only sign up to take a quick look.</p>

<h2>Login</h2>

<%= form_tag sessions_path do %>
	<p>
		<%= text_field_tag :email, params[:email], :placeholder => "email"  %><br />
		<%= password_field_tag :password, "", :placeholder => "password" %>
	</p>
	
	<button type="submit" class="small red awesome">Login</button> or <%= link_to 'join here', join_url %>.
<% end %>
